column5: Has anybody had contact with Robert at Onoman river resort? we have been trying by e-mail, phone and facebook with no luck. Thanks.
I've spoken to him in January, confirming our reservations for this year.FYI he spends winters out West now, so plan a 2-3 hour difference in time from the ETZ if you're calling.
DBH How did you contact him? The phone # I have says not in service.
